tip.text: Set lunch quite worth it by comparing the portion and price. Tastes averagely good. 😊👍
Chasyu Japin Ramen is the bomb! 💣👍👍😋
Orange chocolate latte, black forest cake (MUST TRY) & peanut butter cake (MUST TRY) was really really really good!!! 😍 Definitely will be back again!
Squid ink pasta and chicken clam chowder is really good! 😍😋
Iced dark chocolate mint was really good omg! 😍 Chilled cheese cake was okay. There games to play here too! Small but great place to hang out with friends.
Carbonara set lunch was just okay. Scallops is quite good!
Set lunch is pretty good especially mongolian chicken rice! 🙌😍
The meatballs in beer food platter is sooooooo good omg. Homemade soya is good too! 😋
